name: ''shark boy and mermaid (i dream of you)''
description: a work by Mical Noelson.   12 second video soundscape.  I keep on looking at this guy like I'm growing him in a little fishtank, on the plank scale, between atoms. He just stays there with his trusting smile, clinging on, bobbing around. A little Chimera in a nowhere place in an insignificant moment in time.  I like that he keeps smiling.
